
1. Install Bouyomichan from X
2. Download Aquestalk from Y
3. Install Aquestalk 1 into Bouyomichan subfolder Z
4. Open Win10 Control Panel (search for Control Panel)
5. Open Language+Region settings
6. Select Region Settings
7. Select Administrative Settings
8. Select Change system Locale for programs that do not support unicode
9. Set "Japan".

Restart windows.

Now F1/F2/etc should all work.
